title: Making an active dynamic queue team to climb soloq full of consistant players
body: Im looking to make an active dynamic queue team to climb soloq with full of consistant players who can individually carry  some games but almost never feed in any games. Have to be silver or higher in s6.

replies.body:
I almost made it to gold last season but my team mates always let me down. I'm bronze 3 trying to climb. Never my fault omg. Some people say I have a negative influence but those people just let me down every game. If you cant handle me at my worst, you dont deserve me at my best.

P.S. I only play teemo jg {{champion:17}}

I'm Bronze 5 but I belong in challenger because my teams let me down.
My goal is to get into the LCS this season if I can just find some consistent teams :)
In placements atm but was Gold last season. Add me, just want to have fun with non toxic players :)

sign me up, I main all roles (:
